Package affymetrix.gcos.chp

Class Summary
BackgroundZoneInfo Information about all background zones on an array.
BackgroundZoneType Defines information about a background zone.
BaseCallType Holds a call at a given position.
CHPFileData Provides storage for data in a GCOS CHP file.
CHPFileHeader Stores the contents of the header of a CHP file.
ExpressionProbeSetResults Defines the results for an expression probe set.
ForceCallType A type to hold the force call, the call that the algorithm would have made if the thresholds were relaxed.
GenotypeProbeSetResults Stores results for a genotyping probe set.
ResequencingResults Stores results for a resequencing analysis.
UniversalProbeSetResults Stores results for a universal probe set.
